e":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T14:32:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>佢差過川端康城好多囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好好多唔敢講<br />\n不過村上春樹我只服聽風的歌<br />\n其他川端求其一篇抒情歌都贏佢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇緊山之音，睇得出佢日本文化根底好厚，西學都唔錯<br />\n挪威的森林睇幾頁都唔想睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9549b076f45644446d8261c6b3b69dc9296254c","tid":425111,"uid":42820,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T14:34:09.000Z","msg":"幾時到金庸拎？"},{"pid":"7ad87fa8ced66a3b81a2ae0d2036b7d1a1a4129f","tid":425111,"uid":51978,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T14:38:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾時到金庸拎？</blockquote>agger 根本西人唔識欣賞 無須稀罕"},{"pid":"c00439103d63beef271b489495b5ea2f4203da97","tid":425111,"uid":39013,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T14:39:44.000Z","msg":"我仲以為向西春樹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adda2b47eedcc48d0ae116c48b46275656d7fbc4","tid":425111,"uid":34869,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T14:40:30.000Z","msg":"好心唔預選佢就唔好提名佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8d5cac85cb64d72e5c8742614978f2da0a4f47e","tid":425111,"uid":29625,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T14:42:03.000Z","msg":"俾Bob Dylan都唔俾村上真係好撚on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b65161261489db7a1efdae6582c6c108989495d","tid":425111,"uid":13257,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T14:42:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>幾時到金庸拎？</blockquote>agger 根本西人唔識欣賞 無須稀罕</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都係咁話<br />\n<br />\n我睇左挪威的森林, 真係唔覺有咩咁神"},{"pid":"8a09d13589ad0f63283b4e9b547324eb0a3dc316","tid":425111,"uid":29804,"