ockquote><blockquote>幾時到金庸拎？</blockquote>agger 根本西人唔識欣賞 無須稀罕</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n金庸連提名都唔入圍<br />\n無重量級人馬肯為佢背書推薦俾諾貝爾獎評委會<br />\n亦都<span style=\"color: red;\">無可能過到馬悅然</span>果關 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>此話何解？</blockquote><br />\n評委得佢識中文"},{"pid":"b9b4b39d8cf0297fe4e2a0d0905c6818d860cb4d","tid":425111,"uid":51978,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T16:52:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>幾時到金庸拎？</blockquote>agger 根本西人唔識欣賞 無須稀罕</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n金庸連提名都唔入圍<br />\n無重量級人馬肯為佢背書推薦俾諾貝爾獎評委會<br />\n亦都<span style=\"color: red;\">無可能過到馬悅然</span>果關 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>此話何解？</blockquote><br />\n評委得佢識中文</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢層我知 唔使你講<br />\n咁點解話馬悅然唔會欣賞金庸？"},{"pid":"b548ea4a4e36524f758289ab7d9e3cd3158fa822","tid":425111,"uid":6352,"like":5,"dislike":6,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T16:55:39.000Z","msg":"諾貝爾文學獎根本係笑話，從來無人care"},{"pid":"2d88bbc910e4c0d802fac9af345078472b896e25","tid":425111,"uid":45232,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T17:09:59.000Z","msg":"nobelprize文學獎好多時都係俾啲寫政治野既人<br />\n同埋跨語言黎頒獎根本無意思"},{"pid":"9918204e060b5ee5cf51cdb5b963fa4da36f6169","tid":425111,"uid":44925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T17:13:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好心唔預選佢就唔好提名佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係，好似玩鳩佢咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f86678cc2aacc394efecf8f25a6c6e988228ca1","tid":425111,"uid":34760,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T17:15:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>幾時到金庸拎？</blockquote>agger 根本西人唔識欣賞 無須稀罕</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n金庸連提名都唔入圍<br />\n無重量級人馬肯為佢背書推薦俾諾